{
  "page": "Aglantine",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">Not to be confused with <a href=\"/index.php/Eglantine\" title=\"Eglantine\">Eglantine</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\"><img alt=\"Star of the Faith.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/50px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/75px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/100px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Septa</span><br />Aglantine</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\"><img alt=\"Star of the Faith.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/50px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/75px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/91/Star_of_the_Faith.svg/100px-Star_of_the_Faith.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Moelle_Aglantine_Nysterica_and_Melicent_by_luxmundi-i.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Moelle Aglantine Nysterica and Melicent by luxmundi-i.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/12/Moelle_Aglantine_Nysterica_and_Melicent_by_luxmundi-i.jpg/400px-Moelle_Aglantine_Nysterica_and_Melicent_by_luxmundi-i.jpg\" width=\"400\" height=\"200\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/12/Moelle_Aglantine_Nysterica_and_Melicent_by_luxmundi-i.jpg/600px-Moelle_Aglantine_Nysterica_and_Melicent_by_luxmundi-i.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/12/Moelle_Aglantine_Nysterica_and_Melicent_by_luxmundi-i.jpg/800px-Moelle_Aglantine_Nysterica_and_Melicent_by_luxmundi-i.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Septas <a href=\"/index.php/Moelle\" title=\"Moelle\">Moelle</a>, Aglantine, <a href=\"/index.php/Nysterica\" title=\"Nysterica\">Nysterica</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Melicent\" title=\"Melicent\">Melicent</a> by luxmundi-i</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nSepta</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appendix)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Aglantine</b> is a septa of the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>. She might be one of the <a href=\"/index.php/Most_Devout\" title=\"Most Devout\">Most Devout</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance\">Appearance</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aglantine&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Aglantine has white hair and a sharp face.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aglantine&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aglantine&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Septas  Aglantine, <a href=\"/index.php/Moelle\" title=\"Moelle\">Moelle</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Melicent\" title=\"Melicent\">Melicent</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Nysterica\" title=\"Nysterica\">Nysterica</a> examine <a href=\"/index.php/Margaery_Tyrell\" title=\"Margaery Tyrell\">Margaery Tyrell</a> to see if her <a href=\"/index.php/Maiden\" title=\"Maiden\">maidenhead</a> is still intact, but they find it is not. This is the grounds for Margaery's arrest by the Faith on charges of infidelity.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aglantine&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">When asked if <a href=\"/index.php/Septa\" title=\"Septa\">septas</a> can be members of the <a href=\"/index.php/Most_Devout\" title=\"Most Devout\">Most Devout</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/User:Ran\" title=\"User:Ran\">Ran</a> explained, \"I'm inclined to think that the lack of evidence for them, other than the <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Appendix\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Appendix\">AFFC appendix</a> which seems to have been corrected in <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Appendix\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Appendix\">ADWD</a>, means no.\"<sup id=\"cite_ref-Member_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Member-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aglantine&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Appendix\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Member-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Member_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">asoiaf.westeros.org: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://asoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?/topic/34958-the-asoiaf-wiki-thread/&amp;page=105&amp;tab=comments#comment-8216129\">The ASOIAF wiki thread &#8211; Comment by Ran</a>, August 3, 2018</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\">3.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_43\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 43\">Chapter 43</a>, Cersei X.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405004909\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.083 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.271 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 607/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10823/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7509/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1115/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 1/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2338/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.170/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.67 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  257.256      1 -total\n 83.51%  214.840      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 82.99%  213.484      1 Template:Infobox\n 12.16%   31.272      1 Template:Distinguish\n 10.38%   26.711     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  3.77%    9.690      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  2.42%    6.214      3 Template:Ref\n  1.34%    3.456      3 Template:Ref/core\n  1.03%    2.656      2 Template:References\n  0.70%    1.809      1 Template:Notes\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:6048-0!canonical and timestamp 20260405004909 and revision id 335477\n -->\n",
